description:
Only works with Firefox 3.6+ as far as I care to know, as this uses native gradients; not a single image is used. Doesn't work well with some GM scripts, dAmn Colors included. Colors can however be disabled, and you can set your own using the CSS itself like so (add the "color:" values, .from is for username, .text is for the message body):

.damncr .self-hl .from span 
{
background:-moz-linear-gradient(bottom, #000, #414141 70%)!important;
-moz-border-radius:4px!important;
padding:1px!important;
color:#ffffff!important;
}

.damncr .self-hl .text span 
{
background:-moz-linear-gradient(bottom, #000, #414141 70%)!important;
-moz-border-radius:4px!important;
padding:1px!important;
color:#ffffff!important;
}

These two bits of code can be found near the top of the script.

This was meant to be a gradient practice tool, but I quite like how it turned out, as do others, apparently. So it's somewhat public now. Questions? Catch me on dA (http://i-hate-mushrooms.deviantart.com) or email me at infernowasp@gmail.com; you've more luck getting a response on dA. ;D

I'm proud of this, it's by far the most different chat style I've seen to-date. inb4 pride is a sin

Screenshot here http://i49.tinypic.com/2dwgcc2.gif sorry for the shitty .gif format.

css:
@namespace url(http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml);

@-moz-document domain("chat.deviantart.com")

{

body {
height: 95%!important;
width: 95%!important;
position: relative!important;
top: 0px!important;
left: 2.5%!important;
margin: 0!important;
padding: 0!important;
font-family: Segoe UI !important;
font-size: .85em!important;
background:-moz-linear-gradient(top, #DFFC96, #BCF15C 30%, #527C0C, #44660A)!important;
}

.damncr .self-hl .from span 
{
background:-moz-linear-gradient(bottom, #000, #414141 70%)!important;
-moz-border-radius:4px!important;
padding:1px!important;
}

.damncr .self-hl .text span 
{
background:-moz-linear-gradient(bottom, #000, #414141 70%)!important;
-moz-border-radius:4px!important;
padding:1px!important;
}

a 
{
text-decoration:none!important;
}

.damn-lo-row-top
{
border: 0px solid #fff !important;
background:-moz-linear-gradient(top, #414141, #414141 40%, #000) !important;
}

#bar-deviant-ctrl3 
{
background:-moz-linear-gradient(top, #5C5C5C, #414141 20%, #000) !important;
border: none !important;
}

.damncr-title 
{
color: #BCF15C !important;
background:-moz-linear-gradient(top, #414141, #414141 40%, #000) !important;
}

.damncr-title a 
{
color: #0093FA !important;
}

.damncrc-topic 
{
background:-moz-linear-gradient(top, #414141, #414141 40%, #000) !important;
color: #BCF15C !important;
border: 0px !important;
}

.damncrc-topic a 
{
color: #0093FA !important;
}

.damncrc-chat-window 
{ 
border:none !important; 
}


.damn .alt2, 
.damncrc-input input,
textarea.damncrc-input
{
background-color: transparent !important;
color: #BCF15C  !important;
border-color: #BCF15C !important;
}

.damncrc-chat 
{
background-color: transparent !important;
color: #bcf15c  !important;
}

.damncrc-icon-roomname 
{
color: #BCF15C  !important;
}

.damncr .other-hl .from span 
{
background:-moz-linear-gradient(top, #000, #414141 80%, #5c5c5c) !important;
-moz-border-radius:4px!important;
padding:1px!important;
color:#DFFC96!important;
}

.damncr .other-hl .text span 
{
background:-moz-linear-gradient(top, #000, #414141 80%, #5c5c5c) !important;
-moz-border-radius:4px!important;
padding:1px!important;
color:#DFFC96!important;
}

#bar-user, 
#bar-deviant 
{
border-color: #414141 !important;
}

.damncr-infoctr 
{
border-color: #414141 !important;
-moz-border-radius:7px 0px 7px 0px!important;
background:-moz-linear-gradient(top, #5C5C5C, #414141 20%, #000) !important;
}

.damncri-member .bodyarea 
{
border-color:#000!important;
}

.damncr-infoctr 
{
-moz-border-radius:5px 0px 0px 5px!important;
}

.aside-left, .damncr .userinfo .avatar
{ 
background-color: #000 !important; 
border: 0px !important; 
} 

#bar-deviant-ctrl2, 
#bar-deviant-ctrl1
{
background:-moz-linear-gradient(top, #5C5C5C, #414141 20%, #000) !important;
}

.damncri-member .bodyarea, 
.damncri-member
{
color: #BCF15C  !important;
background:-moz-linear-gradient(top, #5C5C5C, #414141 20%, #000) !important;
border-color:#000;
}

.damncri-member strong a
{
color: #0093FA !important;
}

.damncri-member a
{
color: #0093FA !important;
text-decoration:none!important;
}

.damncri-member .avatar
{
background:-moz-linear-gradient(top, #5C5C5C, #414141 20%, #000) !important;
border-color: #414141 !important;
}

.damncri-member
{
background:#000!important;
}

.damncri-member .bodyarea UL 
{
list-style-type: none!important;
margin: 0!important;
padding-left: 1.2em!important;
border-color: transparent!important;
background:-moz-linear-gradient(top, #000, #414141 80%, #5C5C5C) !important;
}

.alt1-border 
{
border-width:0;
border-style:solid;    
border-color:#000;
}

.alt1-top-border 
{
border-width:0;
border-style:solid;
border-top-color:#000;
}

.alt1-bottom-border 
{
border-width:0;
border-style:solid;
border-bottom-color:#000;
}

.alt0-bottom-border 
{
border-width:0;
border-style:solid;
border-bottom-color:#000;
}

.alt1-left-border 
{
border-width:0;
border-style:solid;
border-left-color:#000;    
}

.damnc-serverlog-outer
{
border:1px solid #000!important;
color:#BCF15C!important;
padding:0.2em 1em 0.15em 0.7em;
background:-moz-linear-gradient(top, #5C5C5C, #414141 20%, #000) !important;
}

.userinfo
{
background:#000!important;
}

.userinfo .connarea
{
margin-top:0.8em;
border:1px solid #000!important;
background:#000!important;
}

.damn-lo-col-right
{
color: #BCF15C  !important;
text-align:right!important;
}

.damn-lo-col-right dt
{
color: #0093FA !important;
margin:15px!important;
background:-moz-linear-gradient(top, #000, #414141 80%, #5c5c5c) !important;
width:150px!important;
text-align:center!important;
border:1px solid #414141!important;
padding:5px!important;
text-shadow:#000 0px 3px 7px,#000 0px 0px 7px;
}

.damncr-members 
{
border-left:1px solid #414141!important;
}

.alt0
{
background:-moz-linear-gradient(top, #5C5C5C, #414141 20%, #000) !important;
}

.damncr .join, 
.damncr .part
{
color: #7C8680 !important;
}
 
.damnc-tabbar a 
{ 
padding: 6px 4px 6px 6px !important; 
margin: 2px 3px 0px 3px !important; 
background:-moz-linear-gradient(top, #787878, #6A6A6A 60%, #5B5B5B 80%, #414141) !important;
-moz-border-radius:7px 0px 0px 0px!important;
height:13px!important;
}

.damnc-tabbar a i { 
background:-moz-linear-gradient(top, #787878, #6A6A6A 60%, #5B5B5B 80%, #414141) !important;
-moz-border-radius:0px 7px 0px 0px!important;
}

.damnc-tabbar a:hover 
{ 
margin: -1px 3px -1px 3px !important; 
background:-moz-linear-gradient(top, #c0c0c0, #787878 60%, #5B5B5B 80%, #414141) !important;
-moz-border-radius:7px 0px 0px 0px!important;
height:16px!important;
}

.damnc-tabbar a:hover i 
{ 
margin: 0px 0px 0px 3px !important; 
background:-moz-linear-gradient(top, #c0c0c0, #787878 60%, #5B5B5B 80%, #414141) !important;
-moz-border-radius:0px 7px 0px 0px!important;
}

.damnc-tabbar strong 
{ 
padding: 6px 4px 7px 8px !important; 
margin: 1px 3px -2px !important; 
background:-moz-linear-gradient(top, #A1D8FF, #0093FA 60%, #0263A6 80%, #414141) !important;
-moz-border-radius:7px 0px 0px 0px!important;
}

.damnc-tabbar strong i 
{ 
background:-moz-linear-gradient(top, #A1D8FF, #0093FA 60%, #0263A6 80%, #414141) !important;
-moz-border-radius:0px 7px 0px 0px!important;
}

.damnc-tabbar strong.withX 
{ 
padding: 6px 24px 7px 8px !important; 
margin: 1px 3px -2px !important; 
background:-moz-linear-gradient(top, #A1D8FF, #0093FA 60%, #0263A6 80%, #414141) !important;
-moz-border-radius:7px 0px 0px 0px!important;
}

.damnc-tabbar strong.withX i 
{ 
background:-moz-linear-gradient(top, #A1D8FF, #0093FA 60%, #0263A6 80%, #414141) !important;
-moz-border-radius:0px 7px 0px 0px!important;
}

.withX img 
{ 
margin-top: 4px !important;
}

.damncr .msg .text a 
{
color: #0066AE !important;
}

.damncr .other-hl .text a 
{
color: #0066AE !important;
}

.chatroom #top
{
margin-top: 0px !important;
background:-moz-linear-gradient(top, #DFFC96, #DFFC96 70%, #527C0C)!important;
}

.chatroom .ch-ctrl 
{
margin: 0 10px !important;
padding: 0 0 0 7px !important;
background: none !important;
border: none !important;
}

#logindock .text
{
color: transparent !important;
margin-top: 1px !important;
}

#logindock .text a
{ 
text-decoration: none !important;
}

#logindock .loginmenu,
#logindock .text a.blend,
#logindock .loginmenu,
#logindock .text a.bling
{
position: absolute !important;
margin-top: -9999% !important;
}

#logindock .text a,
#logindock .text span.a
{
color: #0093FA !important;
}

.chatroom #logindock .text span:first-child
{
display: none !important;
}

#logindock .text span.a:before
{
content: "Hello, " !important;
}

#logindock .text #rockdock-message-count
{
margin-left: 0px !important;
}

#logindock .text #rockdock-message-count a
{
text-transform: lowercase !important;
}

#logindock .text a:hover
{
color: #0093FA !important;
}

.damncrc-chat-inner 
{
background:-moz-linear-gradient(top, #000 5%, #5C5C5C 99.99%, #414141, #000) !important;
border: 1px solid #414141!important;
height: auto!important;
}
}
